Change Log
===========

1.0.2
--------
* Added test for: 'should be able to show an error when try to save with already-existing username'
* Added test for: 'should be able to show an error when try to save without username'
* Added test for: 'should be able to show an error when try to save with email not properly formed'

1.0.1
--------
* Added change log
* Added support for reading environment variables from .env
* Updated Node and npm versions
* Added TravisCI badge to readme
* Added schema for 'Article', making the 'title' field to be required, so that the unit test "should be able to show an error when try to save without title" passes
